# FusionIntel Core (Layer 4–8)

This repository contains a minimal, stable core pipeline:

- **Layer 4**: Sovereignty compliance gate
- **Layer 5**: Delivery action selection (deliver/quarantine/block)
- **Layer 6**: Audit event builder + JSONL writer
- **Layer 7**: Orchestrator pipeline (L4→L5→L6)
- **Layer 8**: CLI (python -m orchestrator.cli)

## Quickstart (Windows / PowerShell)

Run tests:
`powershell
python .\scripts\run_tests.py
python -m pip install -e ".[dev]"
python -m orchestrator.cli --policy policy.json --envelope envelope.json

---

# Step 2 — Run these commands (PowerShell)

`powershell
python -m pip install -e ".[dev]"
python scripts/run_tests.py
git status --short
git add .
git commit -m "Add packaging (pyproject) + README + CI workflow"
git tag v0.1.1
git push
git push origin v0.1.1
gh release create v0.1.1 --title "v0.1.1 – Packaging + CI" --notes "Adds pyproject.toml for editable installs and GitHub Actions CI to run the test suite on push/PR."
pwd
Get-ChildItem pyproject.toml
type pyproject.toml | Select-Object -First 20
python -m pip install -e .[dev]
python -m pip install -e ".[dev]"
function Write-FileUtf8NoBom([string], [string]) {
   = Split-Path -Parent 
  if ( -and !(Test-Path )) { New-Item -ItemType Directory -Force -Path  | Out-Null }
   = New-Object System.Text.UTF8Encoding(False)
  [System.IO.File]::WriteAllText((Resolve-Path .).Path + "\" + , .Replace("
","
"), )
}

Write-FileUtf8NoBom "README.md" @"
# FusionIntel Core (Layer 4–8)

Stable core pipeline:

- **Layer 4**: Sovereignty compliance gate
- **Layer 5**: Delivery action selection (deliver/quarantine/block)
- **Layer 6**: Audit event builder + JSONL writer
- **Layer 7**: Orchestrator pipeline (L4→L5→L6)
- **Layer 8**: CLI (python -m orchestrator.cli)

